      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] Typora</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="typora-plugin">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#typora-plugin"></a>
typora-plugin
</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/obgnail/typora_plugin">https://github.com/obgnail/typora_plugin</a></p>
<h3 id="1-自动编号">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e8%87%aa%e5%8a%a8%e7%bc%96%e5%8f%b7"></a>
1. 自动编号
</h3><p>关闭</p>
<h3 id="2-快捷键中心">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83"></a>
2. 快捷键中心
</h3><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-json" data-lang="json"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nt">&#34;ENABLE&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nt">&#34;NAME&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nt">&#34;HOTKEY&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="nt">&#34;CUSTOM_HOTKEYS&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;enable&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;hotkey&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;ctrl+m&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;desc&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;添加mark&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;plugin&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;function&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;closestSelector&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;evil&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;() =&gt; { const s = window.getSelection().toString(); document.execCommand(&#39;insertText&#39;, false, s ? `&lt;mark&gt;${s}&lt;/mark&gt;` : &#39;&lt;mark&gt;&lt;/mark&gt;&#39;); }&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">},</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;enable&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">true</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;hotkey&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;ctrl+shift+t&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;desc&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;插入hugo的front_matter&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;plugin&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;function&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;closestSelector&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">      <span class="nt">&#34;evil&#34;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&#34;() =&gt; { const d = new Date(); const date = `${d.getFullYear()}-${String(d.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, &#39;0&#39;)}-${String(d.getDate()).padStart(2, &#39;0&#39;)}`; return this.utils.insertText(null, `+++\\n\\ndate = &#39;${date}&#39;\\ndraft = false\\nmath = true\\ntitle = &#39;[x] y&#39;\\ncategories = [&#39;x&#39;]\\ntags = []\\n\\n+++\\n`); }&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="p">]</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="typora-community-plugin">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#typora-community-plugin"></a>
typora-community-plugin
</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/typora-community-plugin/typora-community-plugin">https://github.com/typora-community-plugin/typora-community-plugin</a></p>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-21首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-21</p>]]>
